  skillName: "No\xE3n Hu\u1EC7"
  skillDescription: "Giai \u0111o\u1EA1n k\u1EBFt th\xFAc, b\u1EA1n c\xF3 th\u1EC3
    l\u1EF1a ch\u1ECDn m\u1ED9t ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u01A1i, ng\u01B0\u1EDDi n\xE0y
    c\xF3 th\u1EC3 xem nh\u01B0 s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng X l\xE1 b\xE0i C\u01A1 B\u1EA3n
    (X l\xE0 s\u1ED1 b\xE0i trong khu Trang B\u1ECB c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD v\xE0 t\u1ED1i
    thi\u1EC3u l\xE0 1, n\u1EBFu h\u1ECD s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng b\xE0i c\xF9ng t\xEAn
    b\u1EB1ng c\xE1ch n\xE0y, sau khi ho\xE0n t\u1EA5t k\u1EBFt to\xE1n th\xEC b\u1ECF
    \u0111i to\xE0n b\u1ED9 b\xE0i trong khu Trang B\u1ECB)."
